snippet.title: Plug n Play Games: Disney's Pirates of the Caribbean Islands of Fortune
snippet.description:
Help support the channel: https://www.patreon.com/ZCInfinity


Help Jack Sparrow conquer the Caribbean! Travel to an island, engage in one-on-one sword fighting, dodge traps for treasure, and sink invading fleets of ships! ...Then go to the next island and do it all over again! ...15 times... And people say On Stranger Tides is the most boring thing related to the series...
